      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>
Long time no see, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>. Have you found your Telesia yet?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-1-b" mid="10" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Trust?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>It seems like you have grown much stronger than before. However, I sense that you have incomplete trust in the strength you have.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-1-c" mid="12" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Have you felt that way too? </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>That's right. I can see it in your eyes that you have doubts about whether you're doing well. I see it often in elves who have not found their Telesia yet or are wondering if the Telesia they've found is their true Telesia.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-1-d" mid="14" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>A little help?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>Maybe. I can at least give you a little help, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-1-e" mid="16" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>How can I go there?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>
There is a secret training ground in Saint Haven where you can test your strength. How about going there and testing yourself?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-1-f" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>Talk to me and select [Enter Battle Training Ground]. But you must go alone. It would be meaningless to go to the training ground if you bring friends along.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-1-g" mid="20" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>There is a Half Golem in the Battle Training Ground. He doesn't attack so try whatever skills you want and you may find the best set of consecutive skills.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2" mid="22" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Nod)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>And try achieving more than <FONT color=#a82424>30 combos</FONT> there. When you're done, <FONT color=#a94407>complete the quest in the quest window</FONT>. There is no need for you to come back to me.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-a" mid="24" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>No, I'll go later.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-chk_party" mid="25" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I'm ready.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>I'll send you straight to the Battle Training Ground just this once. Are you ready?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-back_2" mid="27" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Back)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Ithilien$<BR>No problem. Please tell me when you are. All the other masters of different classes know about Battle Training Ground too.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n044_archer_master_ishilien-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
